   306                                  ;  BX POINTS 1 BYTE PAST LAST BYTE PUT IN MEM
   307                                  ;  CX CONTAINS DECREMENTED BYTE COUNT
   308                                  ;  DX CONTAINS NUMBER OF BYTES ACTUALLY READ
   309                                  ;--------------------------------------------
   310                                  fn03:
